// Daily Statistics Endpoints

### Get All Daily Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics

### Get Today's Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/today

### Get Summary (Last 7 Days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/summary

### Get Summary (Last 30 Days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/summary?days=30

### Get Statistics by Date
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/2024-03-12

### Get Statistics by Date (invalid format)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/invalid-date

### Get Statistics Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/range?from=2024-03-01&to=2024-03-12

### Get Statistics Range (invalid dates)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/range?from=invalid&to=invalid

### Create Daily Statistics
POST http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date": "2024-03-13"
}

### Create Daily Statistics (invalid date)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date": "invalid"
}

### Delete Daily Statistics
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/2024-03-13

### Delete Daily Statistics (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/daily-statistics/2099-01-01
